(371, 520, '<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;有很多女性，因为生完孩子。造成胸部下垂，那么该怎么办呢？目前可以通过乳房下垂矫正术来解决，而很多女性想知道，乳防下垂矫正术的效果怎样呢？这个问题，下面我们就来进行了解一下吧。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 乳房下垂矫正的效果怎样？乳房下垂是一种生理现象，常见于生育哺乳后的女性。由于乳房腺体和结缔组织经过增生肥大和萎缩后使乳房的弹性降低，支持韧带拉长，使乳房弹性降低，不仅影响女性的胸部形态，也给工作和生活带来不便，通过手术可将松弛的拉紧，悬吊下垂的乳腺组织，使乳房挺拔。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/2-160602104344461.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 463px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">乳房下垂矫正</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 乳房下垂矫正术的优点在哪呢？</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1、乳房不仅可以得到提升，而且并不会影响到今后的哺乳。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2、乳房变得高挺，提升到适当的位置。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3、乳房不再下垂，而变得丰满高挺起来。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4、如果术后还有任何的要求，都可以进行再次的手术。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 亲，如果您想了解更多，欢迎您拨打我们的免费美丽热线进行了解，我院的咨询医师会给您耐心、详细的解答，并给您一个满意的答复！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px;" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(372, 582, '<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>自体脂肪怎样丰泪沟</strong></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　自体脂肪丰泪沟是借助抽脂仪器抽取身体部位存活率高的脂肪细胞，借助提纯净化仪器</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">处理后，再用专利的脂肪注射定位器将其注射到泪沟凹陷部位，实现理想的丰泪沟效果。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">　　自体脂肪丰泪沟优点</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　1、效果持久。选用先进的水动力吸脂设备抽取脂肪细胞，水动力仪器的钝性针头可以保</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">留脂肪细胞结构的完整性，同时它的同步回收装置可以缩短脂肪细胞暴露在空气里的时间，</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">大限度的提升脂肪细胞的成活率，实现丰泪沟效果。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　2、安全性高。丰泪沟使用三维多层次立体注射技术，分层次、多点、均匀的注射脂肪到</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">泪沟凹陷部位，使得注射部位的皮肤光滑平整，脂肪分布均匀，没有硬块、结节或者脂肪坏</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">死液化的问题。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　3、微创。自体脂肪丰泪沟是用针管注射操作，安全性很高，注射后的痕迹会在一周后消</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">失，注射的创伤小。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602105AW60.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">注射丰泪沟</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">　　玻尿酸怎样丰泪沟</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　玻尿酸可以填充凹陷，增强皮肤的保湿和补水性能，将玻尿酸注射到泪沟部位后，凹陷</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">的皮肤会被填平，泪沟也会消失不见。无论是泪沟、泪沟型黑眼圈，或是血管性黑眼圈，都</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">可以使用施打玻尿酸填补，也有的人为了使眼眶下的苹果肌看起来饱满，而注射玻尿酸。玻</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">尿酸有多种分子量可选择，为达到理想的美容效果，专业医生会选择不同分子大小的玻尿酸</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">、不同的皮肤深度来做施打，有泪沟打玻尿酸是非常好的选择。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">　　玻尿酸丰泪沟优点</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　1、效果自然真实。玻尿酸是液体状态的物质，它可以和皮肤组织好融合，没有凹凸不平</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">或颗粒物残留，触感真实，外观看起来没有破绽。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　2、微创。使用玻尿酸丰泪沟创伤小，不需要剥离眼部皮肤组织结构。对人体的创伤极小</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　3、可逆性。玻尿酸一般会在半年内被人体分解代谢出去，不会长期留存在泪沟部位。即</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">使丰泪沟失败了，也依然可以反悔，变成当初的样子。&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px;" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
(373, 582, '<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;泪沟是指由内眼角开始出现在下眼睑靠鼻侧的一条凹沟，是由于眼眶隔膜下缘的软组织</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">萎缩、下垂而生成的。有的人甚至可延伸到脸颊。由于泪沟的凹陷与周围皮肤的对比映衬，</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">使下睑组织看起来有些臃肿、凸出，由此很容易被认为是眼袋，但其实那只是泪沟变深给人</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">的错觉。　</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602105AW60.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">注射丰泪沟</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;注射丰泪沟的优势</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　泪沟是如何形成的，一般泪沟是先天性的，眼皮较薄的人经常会比一般人更明显。但泪</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">勾通常在年青时不会很明显，这是由于年青人皮下脂肪较为丰富，皮肤也较为紧绷，因此只</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">会有隐约的轮廓。不过，随着年龄的增长，皮下脂肪日渐萎缩，皮肤会变薄并因弹性降低而</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">下垂，下眼皮内侧的泪沟就会变得很明显，眼袋就这样显现出来了。泪沟的出现容易让人有</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">憔悴的印象，而且还让人显得比较衰老，一旦眼周有了泪沟型黑眼圈，会看起来一脸疲乏，</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">似乎没睡好的样子。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">　　泪沟和眼袋的区别</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　泪沟的凹陷在四面皮肤的对比映衬，会使下睑组织看起来有些臃肿、凸出，很轻易被误</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">以为是眼袋，但实在那只是泪沟变深令人产生的错觉。如果从侧面观测，可以比较清楚看出</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">眼袋和泪沟的区别，由于眼袋是有凸出感的，而泪沟则只有凹陷。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px;" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
(374, 582, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;眼睛是人际交往的主要沟通渠道，人们往往会特别注重眼部的美观和保养。但是，护肤</span><span style="font-size: 14px">品终究是挡不住时间的脚步，眼部的各种皱纹让很多美女黯然失色，令人唏嘘不已。那有没</span><span style="font-size: 14px">有什么解决的好方法呢？</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　去除泪沟纹什么方法好？</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　双均整形医师介绍，玻尿酸是人体组织一部分，原本就存在皮肤中，起着锁水保湿的作</span><span style="font-size: 14px">用，所以注射玻尿酸填充泪沟的不会发生的副作用的，效果自然美观。而且由于注射玻尿酸</span><span style="font-size: 14px">使用效果好、十分钟快捷美容无恢复期、安全性高、副作用少，受到许多求美者的喜爱。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602105AW60.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射丰泪沟</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">　　1、有效填充，见效时间快</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　用微量的生物制剂在面部皮下注射，短时间内有效消除面部密集细小皱纹，如泪沟、前</span><span style="font-size: 14px">额、眉间、眼外眦部、颊部、口角、颈部等皱纹，使皮肤光泽有弹性。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　玻尿酸填充泪沟的效果图</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">　　2、不需要恢复期，立刻可以上班</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　注射填充美容是通过生物制剂对皱纹及其支配神经的麻痹作用达到治疗的目的，这种治</span><span style="font-size: 14px">疗不需要恢复期，只要几分钟即可直接回家或去办公室上班。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">　　3、无需开刀，没有不良反应</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　注入的药物数小时就会被人体吸收，所以不必担心对人体的副作用，注射无需手术、微</span><span style="font-size: 14px">痛苦、无不良反映，见效快，安全、简单有效。短短几天就能使皱纹逐渐变浅直至消退，皮</span><span style="font-size: 14px">肤变得平整而光亮，让人看上去年轻十岁左右。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
(375, 582, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 泪沟的出现，让脸部显得不够饱满，也让人的精神大打折扣。爱美女性一旦出现泪沟，多会选择注射玻尿酸填充泪沟，下面来看看双均整形医师对玻尿酸填充泪沟的介绍。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 玻尿酸填充泪沟方法简单。采用注射玻尿酸填充泪沟的方法，需要的手术时间短暂，一般只需要半个小时就可以完成，而且术后恢复很快，由于玻尿酸原本就存在皮肤中，起着锁水保湿的作用，所以注射玻尿酸填充泪沟的不会发生任何的副作用的，效果自然美观。玻尿酸填充泪沟方法很简单，对于泪沟不严重的人是很好的方法，效果持久。虽然效果并非永久，但由于注射玻尿酸时间短，恢复时间短、副作用少，获得许多人的喜爱。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602105AW60.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射丰泪沟</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师指出，注射玻尿酸填充泪沟就是要将凹陷处的地方填补起来。注射玻尿酸填充泪沟可以将鼓出来多于脂肪填补泪沟一举两得，对于有泪沟的人是时常实行的手术，而且还可以起到除皱的效果。玻尿酸填充泪沟是非常安全的，由于玻尿酸本身就是人体含有的成分，但是会随着年纪的增长而逐渐的减少的，玻尿酸流失后，细纹也容易产生。所以玻尿酸也经常被用做平复皱纹，抗衰补湿的美肤材料。注射玻尿酸，不仅触感自然，而且融合度也非常的好。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 通过上述的介绍，相信大家对玻尿酸填充泪沟有了更多的了解，但双均整形医师在此提醒大家，大家一定要到正规的整形医院机构进行整形手术。如果您还有什么疑问，可点击我们的在线咨询或拨打美丽热线电话，我们的医师会为您提供专业的服务。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(376, 582, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;眼睛是心灵的窗户，拥有美丽的双眸是所有人共同的心愿。然而随着时间的流逝我们的泪沟也渐渐凹陷起来使我们不再拥有美丽的双眸。玻尿酸填充泪沟无疑是比较好的方式之一。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　玻尿酸填充泪沟的方法：在泪沟处标记出注射位置，拍照，消毒，再在标记位置皮内注射 2% 利多卡因加肾上腺素 0.03 ～ 0.05ml ，配合轻微指部按压再进行局部麻醉。麻醉后进行真皮内后退式注射，缓慢有序的注入小滴透明质酸，如同一串水珠；退出注射针头，采用均匀强度指压，使注射剂均匀散开；在其余麻醉点进行相同操作直至鼻颊沟和眼眶下区有效治疗；注射后即刻进行轻微的冷敷，嘱受术者 48 小时内避免活动和高温。　</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">　　玻尿酸填充泪沟的优势：</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　1、天然成分：来自于生物组织，因此无异物感及外来物质存留。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　2、简单安全，快速有效：微型整容不用开刀，只需真皮内注射，避免了手术风险，同时微型整容采用局部注射法，因此马上就可以看到效果。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　<img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602105AW60.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射丰泪沟</span></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　3、舒适微痛苦：微型整容采用注射法，像打针一样，局部仅有微胀微痛感，无大痛苦，顾客容易接受。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　4、填充同时也补水：注射过程轻松方便，保湿补水，是当今较佳的保湿产品。　</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">　　玻尿酸填充泪沟，你也可以拥有美丽双眸。现在您相信已经对玻尿酸填充泪沟有了一个比较的了解了。双均医师温馨提示：为了您填充的安全和预期效果好选择正规的整形美容医院进行美容。如果您还有更过疑问欢迎点击咨询双均医师。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
(377, 580, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 注射瘦腿会有副作用吗？瘦腿针也叫(botox瘦小腿)将人体美学与生物工程技术有机的结合，以非手术方式实现腿部形态改变。既能快速美化小腿肌肉发达者，还能持久纤细，不但从医学美容上解决了因肌肉发达而造成的瘦腿难题，更称得上是整形美容历史上的又一创举。下面我们就一起来听听双均整形医师的详细介绍。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形的医师指出，肉毒素注射瘦小腿不需要麻醉，只需要在两侧小腿肌肉肥厚处选择几个注射点，进行适量的注射即可，只需要十多分钟，注射后在针孔处有一些瘀血外，其它没有任何不适，可以从事正常活动。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 瘦腿针其实是只要控制到位安全无害的针剂，在经过人体的新陈代谢之后，当然前提要适量，如果过量的话就会对人体产生副作用。这样看你小腿属于哪种类型。瘦腿针并不是所有人都能够打，要看你的小腿属于哪种类型。医师会根椐你的小腿类型打瘦腿针，不同类型的小腿胖，治疗方法也不尽相同。这就需要有资质的医院医师进行。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602164045a3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射瘦腿</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 肉毒杆菌能破坏一种名为SNAP-25的蛋白质，从而切断神经细胞间的通信使肌肉麻痹。肉毒杆菌的这一功能已被用于治疗斜视和肌肉痉挛等，后来整容医师开始用这种毒素麻痹面部肌肉以达到除皱，瘦腿部肌肉等。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 瘦腿针是现在来说比较安全几乎没有副作用的一种瘦腿方法。而且最大的特点就是无痛苦，它只是在腿部选择几个点来注射，不会给人太大的同感，连麻醉都不必使用。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136');
