(378, 580, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 做注射瘦腿后需要怎样护理？拥有好身材是每个女人的梦想，什么叫做好身材呢？好身材是不是全身上下都要瘦才叫好身材呢？肯定不是，好身材是讲求协调的。比如说一个人上半身胖，下半身瘦，这肯定是不协调的，也是不好看的。不过，腿瘦也是一件值得骄傲的事情，因为很多女孩子的腿很粗壮。下面我们就一起来听听双均整形医师的详细介绍。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形的医师指出，目前，可以选择注射瘦腿的方法效果非常不错。这种瘦腿方法是利用抑制乙醯胆碱的神经传导物质释放，抑制肌肉收缩，从而达到腓肠肌萎缩的效果。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602164045a3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射瘦腿</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 注射肉毒杆菌瘦腿不需要麻醉，只需要在2侧小腿肌肉肥厚处选择几点，进行适量地注射即可，只需10多分钟。进行肉毒杆菌瘦腿手术后恢复快：肉毒素注射后三天就会开始感觉小腿比较没有力量，跑步时，会有点力不从心，但不会影响行走。在注射两周后，就可以感觉小腿曲线的变化，这种变化注射后2个月达到顶点， 效果较好。肉毒杆菌能使腓肠肌萎缩1-1.5公分，效果能维持4-8个月。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 不过为了保证注射肉毒杆菌瘦腿后维持较长时间，做好相应的护理工作是至关重要的，一般来讲，肉毒杆菌瘦腿后的护理主要有：</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1、一周内慎重使用庆大霉素类消炎药。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2、不要按摩，保持正常饮食和作息规律即可，这样做可以使效果长久保持。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3、瘦腿后会感觉到乏力，这都是正常现象，不用感到紧张。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4、患有神经肌肉疾病和处于妊娠及授乳期的人禁注射瘦小腿。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 5、重复注射虽然可以强化和延长疗效，但还是要注意，应该在注射后 3-4个月再进行注射。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 通过以上医师的介绍，相信你对注射瘦腿后该如何护理有所了解了吧！如果你还有任何的疑问，请点击双均的在线医师咨询或拨打双均的美丽热线，也可到院与我院医师面对面进行交流，他们会给你一个满意的答案！</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(379, 580, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 很多爱美人士都因为肌肉型的小腿而十分困扰，那么，该如何告别肌肉型小腿呢？</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1、逛街久了小腿会累</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 女人逛街虽然很凶猛，逛上几小时不累，但是真的逛久了，腿还是会酸的，如果逛街之后是小腿比较酸，那么说明走路的时候都是小腿在用力，所以小腿会是肌肉型的。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602164045a3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射瘦腿</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2、曾经骑单车很久</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 上学的时候会骑自行车，自行车如果座位的高度和脚踩的方式不同，那么就容易形成肌肉型小腿，上学的时候几年的踩车时间，就会让你的小腿变成肌肉型的。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师表示，肌肉型小腿，可以通过注射瘦腿针来达到瘦腿的效果。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师提醒广大爱美人士，注射瘦腿针瘦腿一定要选择一家正规专业的整形医院，因为医生的技术和产品的质量最直接的影响着注射瘦腿针后的效果呈现。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切关于美的需求，求美者都可以在双均找到答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
(380, 580, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 纤细修长的小腿是每个爱美的女人都羡慕并渴望拥有的，完美腿型可以令你不必为了让粗腿伪装起来，而穿的遮遮掩掩，那么让腿瘦下来就是急需做到的。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 那么如何能快速拥有纤细修长的小腿呢？据双均整形医师介绍，小腿部出现粗壮分两种情况，一是脂肪堆积导致小腿粗，另外一种就是小腿部肌肉过多导致小腿粗壮。前一种情况，选用吸脂瘦小腿，效果是非常理想。对于肌肉型小腿，吸脂方法是十分不适合的，因为肌肉型粗小腿要去掉的是肌肉，并非脂肪，所以选用注射肉毒素才是合适的方法。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602164045a3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射瘦腿</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师指出，注射肉毒素瘦小腿的原理在于，利用肉毒素杀死腿部部分肌肉神经，然后使肌肉无力收缩，接着肌肉会萎缩，也从而达到腿部塑形瘦掉小腿的目的。这种方法现在也是明星常用的，因为肉毒素瘦小腿是一种无创手术，术后无疤痕，一小针就能让你轻松拥有纤细美腿，手术后见效快，恢复期短，可以说是瘦身于无形之中。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp;但是，由于肉毒素含剧毒，这就要求手术医生专业技术过硬，在注射剂量方面严格把关。因为国家对于肉毒素的注射剂量是有规定的，超过规定的量，有可能会对人的健康构成威胁。所以，一定要选择正规的医院，找专业的医生做手术，才能保障术后的形体效果。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp;一切关于美的需求，求美者都可以在双均找到答案。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(381, 580, '<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 注射瘦腿快速告别&ldquo;大象腿&rdquo;？纤纤细腿是每个爱美女性的梦想，如小腿过粗的被称为大象腿，让很多人觉得自卑，怎么样能够改善这种尴尬的局面呢，瘦腿针是如今减肥方法当中的一种，瘦腿针在层出不穷的瘦身手段中一枝独秀，吸引了众多爱美女士的目光，它能够帮助女士们塑造完美的腿型，让您的美腿更具有魅力。 下面我们就一起来听听双均整形医师的详细介绍。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师指出，瘦腿针是利用注射的方法进行瘦腿，创伤性很小，注射瘦腿针的恢复时间非常短，是一种快速瘦腿的理想方法，可以帮助爱美人士达到理想的瘦腿效果。注射瘦腿针虽然是美容减肥的一种方式，但是只需要直接注射，不需要开刀、不需手术、没有创伤、没有疤痕，而且见效快。可以用短的时间让小腿变得匀称、饱满、真实、自然、协调。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160602/160602/2-160602164045a3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px; cursor: default" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">注射瘦腿</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 注射botox瘦腿针原理和注射瘦脸一样要作用于肌肉组织，阻断神经与肌肉的神经冲动，让过度收缩的肌肉松弛，麻痹过于发达的肌肉，它是利用麻痹肌肉来达到；失用性萎缩；的目的，使的原本肥厚增生的肌肉缩小。这种瘦小腿的方法简单、安全且有效果，也是爱美女性最能接受的方法。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 打botox瘦腿采用的是不开刀、定量、非手术注射的方法，无需麻醉，治疗只需十几分钟即可完成注射瘦腿。注射瘦腿针后不用做按摩或其他护理，不影响正常生活、工作，不开刀、不手术、随做随走，无须恢复期，瘦腿后效果自然，美观。非常适合忙碌于都市生活中的求美者。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 瘦腿针是专门针对小腿肌肉的一种瘦腿方法，效果十分显着，注射几天后就能看到小腿肌肉一天比一天缩小的效果，一般来说瘦腿针的成效可以持续半年以上，而且瘦腿过程中没有任何手术创伤，治疗后恢复的速度也很快。几个月以后，可以巩固注射，这样瘦腿的效果会更持久一些。</span></div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px; cursor: default" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(382, 519, '<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师介绍，女人都希望自己可以拥有一对性感迷人的乳房，看起来漂亮而妩媚。但是亚洲女性的胸部多偏向于平扁，所以如何拥有丰满的胸部是很多女性朋友关注的问题。不过采取自体脂肪隆胸是一种胸部塑形是一个很不错的方法哟！那么，自体脂肪隆胸会留疤吗？</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 医师讲解说，自体脂肪丰胸术绝对属于绿色隆胸术，由于隆胸手术是采用自身的脂肪，所以安全性很高，正常情况都不会对自身发生排异现象。而且隆胸受术者不需要对手术的安全性有负担，该自体脂肪隆胸手术是将隆胸者本身的多余脂肪用细针吸出，在通过仪器活化办理成纯净脂肪颗粒，将脂肪在微型管针分条理均匀注入隆乳区使之成活。是一种不开刀、不出血，同时又达到了减肥塑身的成效的隆胸手术。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160603/2-160603103505222.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 359px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">自体脂肪隆胸</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 那么，自体脂肪隆胸会留疤吗？双均整形医师指出，自体脂肪隆胸手术几乎是无损伤的，它既不需要开刀，也不会留下疤痕。因此经过自体脂肪隆胸术后基本感觉正常，没有痛苦。另外，由于它采用爱美者自身的脂肪组织，因此术后还不会有排异现象，并且手感非常自然，就连亲密的人也很难发现。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均整形医师提醒说，如果一些求美者选择非正规进行，隆胸是会有危害的，如果操作不当或者是护理上没有重视，会出现伤口感染，伤口会发红，隆出的胸部过高或过低等不良现象。这些其实都是失败的隆胸手术，其原因有很多种，不正规、医师没经验、服务团队不专业以及手术实施不先进等都会造成负面影响。因此为了避免上述问题，想要做隆胸的爱美人士一定要到正规权威的医疗进行，这样方可保证效果和安全。如果想了解更多美丽讯息，可以通过以下方式与双均整形的医师取得联系，医师会给你更详细的解答。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px;" /></span></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.100.62'),
(383, 519, '<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;自体脂肪隆胸好不好面对社会上身材丰满傲人的女性，很多身材并不突出的女性往往会很自卑，为了改变这种现状，就去选择丰胸，从而使自己的人生有了翻天覆地的变化，让女性也找回了青春，也重新收货了自己的幸福。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;自体脂肪隆胸好不好？医师介绍，自体脂肪隆胸是抽取身体其他部位，如臀部，腹部等多余的脂肪，进行萃取纯化，然后注射到胸部，通过注射填充，让胸部变得丰满。因为采用的是自体脂肪，所以不会有出现排斥性。可以非常安全的达到隆胸的效果。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　自体脂肪隆胸将隆胸者本身的多余脂肪用细针吸出，活化办理成纯净脂肪颗粒，通过微型管针分条理均匀注入隆乳区使之成活。不开刀、不出血，丰胸成效真实自然，同时又达到了减肥塑身，具有减肥丰胸的效果。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;"><img alt="" src="/uploads/160603/2-160603103505222.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 359px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">自体脂肪隆胸</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">　　自体脂肪隆胸的优点如下：</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　1、采用微创技术提取脂肪的方法，并发症少的吸脂技术，而不同于传统的切除大块脂肪组织或肌肉等方法。因为传统方法可能会造成供区的缺损及留下明显的疤痕。该吸脂术所取切口一般约3-5mm，故愈合后疤痕非常小且位于隐蔽部位(如脐部、阴毛内、臀线等)。对局部脂肪堆积较多的人，可以说即瘦身又隆胸，一举两得。由于术后吸收率在30%-50%，一般需要2-3次方可达到预期效果。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　2、不会引起人体的内分泌环境的改变，自体脂肪隆胸对乳腺本身不会产生伤害，对今后的生育、哺乳，不会有不良的影响。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　3、脂肪移植后的乳房，手感柔软，形态真实，肌肤细腻，从女性及她的伴侣的心理感受来说，对用自体脂肪隆胸增大的乳房的真实感受更好，患者及其伴侣更易接受。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">　　自体脂肪隆胸好不好对于丰胸，女性一定要抱有一个清醒的头脑，切不可盲目的丰胸，虽说丰胸的危害小，但是如果丰胸方法不对就会影响女性的健康。甚至造成切除乳房的危险，所以理性丰胸一直是整容界推崇的理念。&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/160516/2-160516105F3434.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 250px;" /></div>\r\n', '', '', '171.91.101.136'),
