(602, 555, '<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 纹眉的效果能维持多久？人们都说眼睛是灵魂的窗口，那么为了让这扇窗更加魅力，眉毛的作用也非常重要。眼妆中眉毛的修饰给容貌增色不少，可是很多mm们没有精力每天化妆，那么纹眉就是一个很好的选择。不过有求美者疑惑，纹眉的效果能维持多久呢？双均整形美容的纹绣师为大家介绍。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/160615/160615/2-1606151413054b.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 359px;" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;纹眉的效果能维持多久？双均整形美容纹绣师介绍纹眉的效果</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、远看：眉型自然、漂亮、浓淡适宜、清秀，神采奕奕，富于立体感，而充满活力。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、中看（距5米左右）：眉似&ldquo;画的眉&rdquo;，给人以柔和，两侧对称，浓淡相宜、自然又美丽的观感。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、近看：用手触摸时不沾污皮肤，不退色，才知道&ldquo;原来不是画的眉，而是纹的眉&rdquo;的感觉，令人感到柔和、自然、不虚假。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 纹眉的效果能维持多久？纹眉的效果是肯定的，不过究竟它能保持多长时间需要根据实际情况来决定。然后纹眉保持的时间长短跟您选择的色料有一定的关系。所以说纹眉保持的时间长短也是有外界因素影响的！不过一般来说可以管2-3年。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;纹绣师说纹眉虽然简单，但是手术后的护理也还是不能少的，因为纹眉过后肯定会有疼痛感的，所以要好好护理。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 纹眉后的注意事项：</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一、纹眉后可在红肿处进行冷敷，使其尽快消肿，冷敷时应将冰块放置于冰袋内，外裹消毒毛巾进行冷敷20-30分钟，切忌不得将冰袋或冰块直接放于创面上，防止冰水渗透伤口造成感染。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;二、纹眉后在创面上外用消炎(如唇宝、芦荟胶)以防止感染，逐日3次连续三天。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;三、纹眉后的红肿严重的可口服消炎(一般作过重睑术者纹后红肿严重)。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;四、纹眉后三日内创面保持清洁干燥，不得沾水。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;五、结痂后不宜接触热水、蒸汽等，防止痂软化、脱落，影响着色。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;以上就是双均整形纹绣师对纹眉的相关介绍，如果您有任何的疑问或问题，欢迎点击我院的在线咨询医师进行了解，也可拨打我院的美丽咨询热线进行咨询，我们将竭诚为您服务！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一切对美的追求，求美者都将会在双均找到满意的答案！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nb