(639, 632, '<div class="label-box" style="margin: 40px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13px; color: rgb(14, 14, 13); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; position: relative; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span class="label-box-txt bgrded" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; position: relative; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(137, 108, 73); font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgba(145, 103, 38, 0.0980392);">祛胎记</span></div>\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(147, 115, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n				<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n						<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104J53G.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 640px; height: 400px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</div>\r\n						&nbsp;　　祛胎记是利用高强度的激光照射胎记部位，激光瞬间产生高能量，将胎记的色素颗粒崩解汽化，由体内吞噬细胞吞噬，之后随着人体新城代谢排除体外，色素会随之消失，从而达到去除胎记的目的。\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　太田痣治疗后</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104K1626.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 567px; height: 207px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　鲜红斑痣治疗后</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104KU60.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 568px; height: 310px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">咖啡斑治疗后</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104PBK.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 566px; height: 232px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　双均治疗胎记美学设计提醒</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104Q3405.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 640px; height: 526px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均祛胎记</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　见效率高</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　为顾客设定三次&ldquo;Q核&rdquo;激光的治疗，胎记都能够有效击碎。&ldquo;Q核&rdquo;激光治疗期间的IPL光学嫩肤，可巩固治疗效果，面部肌肤水疗及专业基因修护敷膜组合，能够有效缓解激光治疗所带来的不适，保护敏感肌肤，逐步改善肤质。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　祛胎记的同时改善肤质</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　双均祛胎记能对皮下组织产生光热原理，刺激胶原纤维新生，促进肌肤血液循环，提高肌肤光泽度，高效肤质。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　祛胎记低反复</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　综合运用激光、光子、复合光波等进行针对性治疗。真正祛除皮肤胎记问题。 治疗+医学修复+专业保养 为一体的全新组合祛胎记理念。针对不同肤质，达到你想要的效果。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　深层修复肌肤</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　通过渗透技术将营养素直接作用于受损皮肤，有效促进太田痣部位细胞新陈代谢，补充肌肤光洁所需的营养，强效修复肌肤，让皮肤美白有光泽，治疗在1小时内即可完成，不影响工作、学习。</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
