xt-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一步认清痘痘类型 分型而治<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q200604.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 363px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　在临床根据病情的轻重采用Pillsbury分类法将痤疮分为Ⅰ-Ⅳ度<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　Ⅰ度 轻度痤疮</strong></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q209D9.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 526px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　Ⅱ度 中度痤疮</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q21K94.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 780px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　Ⅲ度 重度</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q226229.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 524px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q234M9.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 532px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　Ⅳ度 重度-集簇性</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q241P0.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 528px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q250344.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 567px;" /></strong></p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br class="Apple-interchange-newline" />\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1');
