(643, 636, '<div class="label-box" style="margin: 40px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13px; color: rgb(14, 14, 13); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; position: relative; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span class="label-box-txt bgrded" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; position: relative; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(137, 108, 73); font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgba(145, 103, 38, 0.0980392);">纹眉</span></div>\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(147, 115, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;　<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101F049296.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 291px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				看运在眉</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101F05A37.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 270px; height: 415px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　眉毛代表一个人的运气，眉形的好坏直接关乎一个人的精气神。好的眉毛多而有型，中间不宜间断，并且长过眼睛。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　好气色，从开运眉开始</strong></p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101F106491.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 300px; height: 270px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101F114395.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 300px; height: 270px;" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</strong><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101F121543.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 139px;" />　　</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　纹眉三天后案例对比<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none !important; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;">我要马上蜕变</a><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; 