(648, 635, '<div class="label-box" style="margin: 40px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13px; color: rgb(14, 14, 13); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; position: relative; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span class="label-box-txt bgrded" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; position: relative; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(137, 108, 73); font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgba(145, 103, 38, 0.0980392);">脂肪移植</span></div>\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(147, 115, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n				<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n						<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150555307.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</div>\r\n						&nbsp;　　随着年龄的渐长，面部不可避免地衰老，额头、太阳穴、脸颊等逐渐出现了凹陷、皱纹，胸部也渐渐的萎缩。另一方面由于不正确的生活习惯，身上也囤积了不少的脂肪，样样让人痛不欲生。\r\n						<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150603427.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 282px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</div>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均&mdash;自体脂肪鲜活移植<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150611392.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 520px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　双均自体脂肪鲜活移植，从人体自身某些部位吸取多余的皮下脂肪细胞，纯化处理后注射到额部、胸部，苹果肌，就能立马立体五官，魔鬼身材，完美说明放对地方，脂肪就能变废为宝!<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均自体脂肪移植 取于自体取悦自己</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　1、遇见更精致的自己</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150620340.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 490px; height: 262px;" /></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　一改刻薄不易亲近的印象，饱满太阳穴，让面部轮廓线条感十足。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051015062O27.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 484px; height: 259px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　玻尿酸无法匹及的终身效果，大胆说出我的鼻子完全自体。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101506354P.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 245px;" />　</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							从细微处改变面部风水，一步丰耳垂，整体好印象。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　2、遇见更年轻的自己</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101506433R.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 276px;" />　</span></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　自体脂肪丰眉弓后，即使你的眼睛不够大， 睫毛不够长，依旧会给人曲线清晰的轮廓美。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150A1Z3.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 189px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							　　自体活细胞面部填充可塑造饱满脸颊， 轻松拥有少女粉嫩气质。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150FEa.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 196px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							　　苹果肌又称为笑肌，年轻的时候，比较明显，自体脂肪丰苹果肌， 可以恢复年轻时的饱满，提高面部饱和度。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　3、遇见更性感的自己</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150G6341.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 488px; height: 259px;" /></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　增加腰臀衔接、臀腿衔接的设计，让腰臀腿部曲线更加圆润。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150H6438.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 490px; height: 279px;" /></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　不论婚前产后，术后乳房增大1.5-2个罩杯 ，形态真实，手感柔软细腻， 对生育和哺乳毫不影响。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均自体脂肪鲜活移植优势<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150I5321.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 255px; height: 256px;" /></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　抽取技术：鲜活提取</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　选择较好的脂肪供应区，对脂肪进行鲜活提取创新科技处理，全程采用先进的去脂设备和国外网状超平吸脂技术，安全快速提取具活力优质脂肪颗粒。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150J3105.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 255px; height: 256px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　活化技术：鲜活提炼</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　吸脂后对脂肪进行鲜活提炼创新处理，全面激活脂肪颗粒，使其拥有高度的生物活性，从而具备高度的修复能力和再生能力。确保一次鲜活移植，脂肪成活率就能达到95%以上。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150K0526.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 255px; height: 25