list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 什么是BOTOX?</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G42942463.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 403px;" /></strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; BOTOX是先进得到中国SFDA批准的A型肉毒素针剂，并率先进驻双均.注射BOTOX瘦脸可有效用于治疗食性肌肉肥大，它能够迅速使营养 过剩的肌肉失去部分来自于神经的营养作用，从而让肌肉组织变平、变细，从而达到快速瘦脸的目的，同时注射肉毒素祛皱，还能帮助您消除因为动力而引起的所有 抬头纹、皱眉纹、鱼尾纹，您可以专心思索问题，更自信地笑尽情地表达情感。成为众明星的值得选择瘦脸法宝，同时，BOTOX注射还可用于治疗小腿肌肉肥 大，效果一样无可媲美。</p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; BOTOX除皱原理</strong>：通过阻断神经与肌肉的神经冲动，适度抑制、收缩肌肉作用的神经，从而起到减弱肌肉力量，消除皱纹的作用。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G432025W.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 287px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155341306.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 635px; height: 425px;" /></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; BOTOX瘦脸原理</strong>：将肉毒毒素注射到咬肌内，通过抑制神经肌接头处乙酰胆碱递质的传递，让咬肌逐渐萎缩而起到瘦脸的效果。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G4343A08.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 251px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G43353T5.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 325px;" /></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">BOTOX瘦腿原理</strong>：Botox瘦腿针就是把Botox肉毒素注射入小腿肌肉，从而让小腿肌肉萎缩缩小，它可以针对那些因为小腿肌肉肥大导致的小腿粗壮，有效将小腿瘦下来。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155621337.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 635px; height: 425px;" /></div>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均BOTOX注射美容的优势：</strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 瘦脸瘦腿紧致肌肤</strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均BOTOX功能强大，用于瘦脸、瘦小腿、除皱治疗均能达到好效果。</p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 先进美学设计坐诊</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155P34Z.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 337px;" /></strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均先进非手术美容美学设计亲诊，治疗效果，放心。</p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 随做随走，快速见效</strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗时间短，注射仅需10分钟，24小时内便可见效。</p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 无恢复期 不影响工作</strong></p>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗过程轻松，伤、迹，曲线柔和、效果自然。</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1');
