(655, 620, '<div class="label-box" style="margin: 40px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13px; color: rgb(14, 14, 13); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; position: relative; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span class="label-box-txt bgrded" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; position: relative; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(137, 108, 73); font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgba(145, 103, 38, 0.0980392);">假体隆鼻</span></div>\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(147, 115, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n				<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n						<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144644112.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 308px;" />&nbsp;　　<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">如何选择适合自己的假体?</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</div>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　目前常用的隆鼻材料分为膨体与硅胶两种，一般来说，鼻背皮肤比较薄的，可以用膨体隆鼻。材料的具体选择还是要根据专业医师的面诊情况来选择。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均假体隆鼻恢复过程</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144A3509.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 238px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144F2J3.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 236px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均不同隆鼻材料手术注意事项?</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1、硅胶隆鼻</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144G0917.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 274px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144GQ23.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 226px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　2、膨体隆鼻</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144HG48.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 274px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509144I5254.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 552px; height: 250px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">双均隆鼻手术原则</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　1、选择适合顾客的手术方法</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　根据每个患者的特征做不同的手术方法，选择漂亮的鼻部曲线，给您提供满意的手术效果。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　2、选择肤质和鼻子的模样相配的安全填充物</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　鼻部皮肤或厚、或薄、或透亮，鼻梁的骨质情况也各不相同，双均根据多样化的人体特征选择适合的硅胶、字体、筋膜材料进行恰当的组合，将效果优化。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　3、强调和润挺翘的鼻尖风格。</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　无论做任何鼻部项目，都注重鼻尖形态的塑造。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　4、为了减少炎症发生，配备彻底的灭菌、消毒系统。</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　双均所有手术道具都通过高压灭菌和气体消毒处理。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　5、尽量限度减少疤痕</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							　　尽量采用使开刀的疤痕看不见或缩小的方法进行手术，手术后照顾到减轻疤痕的问题。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							&nbsp;</p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　6、尽量减少组织受损，一同解决浮肿问题，把恢复时间缩到很短。</strong></p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(656, 621, '<div class="label-box" style="margin: 40px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 13px; color: rgb(14, 14, 13); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; position: relative; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n	<span class="label-box-txt bgrded" style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; position: relative; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(137, 108, 73); font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgba(145, 103, 38, 0.0980392);">腰腹吸脂</span></div>\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls" style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(147, 115, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 215, 202);">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510112151446.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;">\r\n				腹部皮肤松弛后很容易长肉，是年纪越大越不能减的部位。腹部是脂肪堆积很容易的部位，吸脂术后可以获得很好的效果，给女性带来光滑柔美的线条。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051011215X95.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 253px; height: 381px;" /></div>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				射频溶脂技术</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　通过腹部吸脂来解决的腹部肥胖，不可以减少腹部脂肪细胞的数量，而且对各种人疾病的预防也有很大的帮助。腹部吸脂的手术部位和切口部位<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　吸脂后，人体内大脂肪细胞数目大大减少，只要求美者不暴饮暴食并进行适度的运动;吸脂塑身的效果可以一直保持下去、不会出现反弹。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　适应人群</strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　腰腹部大量脂肪堆积(水桶腰)</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　产后腰腹部皮肤松弛(游泳圈)</p>\r\n			<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: left; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n				　　躯体中部突出，无身体曲线感等</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
