2);">\r\n				<div class="commitment-content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">\r\n					<div class="txt clearfix" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n						<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605100U643I8.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 313px;" />&nbsp;　　<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">女性常见胸部困扰<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none;" />\r\n							<img alt="" src="http://www.dzsjmr.com/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605100UA1351.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; border: 0px none; display: block; width: 500px; height: 297px;" /></strong></div>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 65); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n							<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">　　双均一站式韩式假体丰胸</strong></p>\r\n						<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; text-decoration: none; outline: none; list-style-type: none; text-align: center; color: rgb(66, 66, 6