(684, 625, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">注射丰下巴</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;　　<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051016112cP.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	面部黄金比例|缺不了精致下巴</strong></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	　　面部黄金比例&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;三庭五眼&rdquo;&ldquo;四高三低&rdquo; 注射丰下巴可以帮你重塑漂亮的下巴，让你的 脸型更加好。</div>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>微整形丰下巴</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　采用玻尿酸等注射材料，将下巴稍微加长，脸型有明显拉有效果，让面部轮廓更加明显。　<br />\r\n	　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051016113D35.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 208px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>真人注射过程　<br />\r\n	　</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161143221.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 200px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161150A8.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 253px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>注射丰下巴注意事项</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　1、治疗前，请保持肌肤的清洁，建议使用洁面乳和收敛水来清洁皮肤。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　2、治疗前3&mdash;4天内，不要服用消炎药(如阿司匹林等)，因为其有可能会加剧注射部位出血和肿胀。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　3、在注射治疗后1-2周内，不要用手指或其他物体按压注射部位。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4、在治疗后至少两周内，不要接触高热环境(如桑拿等)，避免面部注射的透明质酸被快速分解，从而缩短填充效果。</span></p>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(685, 625, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">注射丰额头</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161415937.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;　　从长相来看，额头饱满光亮的女人，给人感觉确实要有贵气一些。如果额头过平或凹陷，则给人一种精神不佳的感觉，通过额部填充可以得到良好的改善。</div>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<br />\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101614225N.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 256px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　额部美丽标准</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　1.平坦微向上突起，柔和平稳过渡至鼻部<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　2.弧度优美流畅，鼻额角135度左右<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　3.额部至鼻尖柔和自然的S形曲线<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>双均注射丰额方法</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　玻尿酸丰额头</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160515/1-1605151SKO93.jpg" style="width: 470px; height: 500px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>术后效果：</strong>效果立现，表情自然，损伤小恢复快<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>注射时间：</strong>注射过程10分钟、即刻见效。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>维持时间：</strong>6-8个月左右(根据个人体质时间是不相同的)<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<a>想要拥有圆润额头?点击咨询</a><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　丰额头&mdash;有效有效</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160515/1-1605151S641241.jpg" style="width: 478px; height: 237px;" /></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>术后效果：</strong>安全、有效、持久、自然</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	　　<strong>注射时间：</strong>注射时间10分钟、即刻见效。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	　　<strong>维持时间：</strong>3~5个月</p>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(686, 625, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">注射丰太阳穴</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;　<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161HDN.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	太阳穴凹陷原因</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　太阳穴部位，在医学上称之为&ldquo;颞&rdquo;。颞部凹陷的人影响脸形上半部分的轮廓。很多上了年纪的老人们更是觉得太阳穴凹陷的人，不好相处、尖酸刻薄。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161I4626.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 500px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>双均丰太阳穴</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均丰太阳穴，主要采用注射填充的方式，将相关材料如玻尿酸等填充到凹陷部位，从而达到抚平凹陷，塑形美容的目的。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161J09B.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 321px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　双均注射优势　　</strong></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510161J91b.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 132px;" /></div>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(687, 625, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">注射丰面颊</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-1605121QZ0935.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" />&nbsp;　　<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	面部凹陷原因</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　面颊凹陷属于先天性遗传因素造成，但更多的是因为年龄的原因，面部消瘦有凹陷不仅看起来没有精神,也比同龄人更显苍老。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　玻尿酸注射丰面颊</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>注射效果：</strong>安全、自然、手感真实、表情更自然<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>注射时间：</strong>注射过程10分钟、即刻见效<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>维持时间：</strong>6-8个月左右(根据个人体质时间是不相同的)</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510162025L3.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 331px;" /></div>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(688, 627, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>注射去法令纹</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510162232944.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" />&nbsp;　　<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	法令纹形成原因</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　法令纹是由面颊部有动力的组织和无动力的组织相互作用的结果而形成。　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510162240143.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 310px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 祛法令纹的方法</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均注射美学设计通过玻尿酸、BOTOX、等各种注射除皱，使法令纹变平、变浅，人立即显得年轻、漂亮。<br />\r\n	　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051016224Q58.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 169px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051016235SB.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 154px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<strong>注射祛法令纹过程　　</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051016232E43.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 195px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101623334M.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 193px;" /></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<blockquote style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</blockquote>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(689, 627, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>注射去抬头纹</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;　<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-1605121631241Z.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 401px;" />　<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	抬头纹产生的原因</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　抬头纹的产生与面部表情有着很大关系，皮下纤维组织的弹性也会逐渐降低，表情挤压到额部皮肤则会习惯性的留下痕迹，次数多了以后便成为顽固的真性皱纹。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150818/1-150QQ31301356.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 311px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>祛抬头纹的方法</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均注射美学设计通过玻尿酸、等各种注射除皱，填充修复皱纹，具有、快速、无需恢复期等优势，能有效解决祛额头纹衰老问题。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<strong>适宜人群 </strong>适用于皮肤张力失去弹性，前额出现皱 纹的人群。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150818/1-150QQ31312308.jpg" style="width: 377px; height: 406px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>注射祛抬头纹过程</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150818/1-150QQ3131Q36.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 193px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160516/2-160516150409B6.jpg" style="width: 572px; height: 220px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>真人案例展示　<br />\r\n	　</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150818/1-150QQ31332462.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 211px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150818/1-150QQ31340542.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 211px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(690, 627, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>注射去川字纹</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-16051216333EZ.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" />　　<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	川字纹形成原因</strong></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　随着年龄增长，面部皱纹逐渐加深，双眉间形成较深的皱折，呈现&ldquo;川&rdquo;字，川字纹一旦形成，会使人看起来总是愁眉不展。　　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://m1.bjyestar.com/zt/wz_qmjw/images/qmcw_03.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 310px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>祛川字纹的方法</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均注射美学设计们通过玻尿酸、等各种注射除皱，填充修复皱纹，具有、快速、无需恢复期等优势，能有效解决祛川字纹衰老问题，让面部看起来更年轻。　<br />\r\n	　</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://m1.bjyestar.com/zt/wz_qmjw/images/qmcw_07.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 173px;" /></div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://m1.bjyestar.com/zt/wz_qmjw/images/qmcw_09.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 151px;" />　</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	真人案例对比</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://m1.bjyestar.com/zt/wz_qmjw/images/qmcw_12.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 149px;" />　<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://m1.bjyestar.com/zt/wz_qmjw/images/qmcw_14.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 149px;" /></div>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(691, 632, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">祛雀斑</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-16051110042NY.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 253px;" /><br />\r\n		<strong>双均祛雀斑的效果</strong></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>表皮层雀斑：</strong>治疗1次<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100434222.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 274px;" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>深皮层雀斑：</strong>治疗3次<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100613518.jpg" style="width: 574px; height: 311px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>深皮层雀斑：</strong>治疗3次<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100621H9.jpg" style="width: 574px; height: 314px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>表皮层雀斑：</strong>治疗2次<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100629208.jpg" style="width: 574px; height: 312px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>双均祛雀斑为什么会不反弹</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　高效的强脉冲能量能够有效找准斑源，有效击碎病变组织里的色素，仅6纳秒瞬间有效穿透表皮到达病变组织，直击斑根，有效清除雀斑且不反弹。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-16051110063Q43.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 169px;" /><br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100645115.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 169px;" /><br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100A2N5.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 169px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　只有做到这3步 才能有效祛除</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>1、皮肤检测</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	　用VISIA皮肤检测，根据不同的肤质，检测你的雀斑是处于表皮层斑，还是深皮层，处于表皮层的雀斑，治疗3次即可，如果处于深皮层治疗次数需要4-5次，才能有效祛除不再反复。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100A9353.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 341px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　2、击破黑色素</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　532纳米激光直接打入皮肤内层100um处，击破黑色素细胞，激光只被相应颜色的色素吸收，只有病变的细胞才吸收特定的激光，所以对皮肤组织没有损伤。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100F6317.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 336px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　3、美肤</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　祛雀斑同时促进胶原再生，收缩毛孔，根据深浅程度治疗后雀斑逐渐消失，皮肤干净白暂，细腻光滑。治疗后不影响出门及工作。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100G3P6.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 343px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　双均祛雀斑治疗过程</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　做完皮肤检测判断属于表皮雀斑</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100H3435.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 314px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　敷祛斑专用麻药</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100I15J.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 317px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　采用纳米激光打掉全脸的雀斑</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100I9141.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 316px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　因为皮肤干燥7天后来做快速水氧护理</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100JJ52.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 316px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　做完快速后的效果</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511100K4241.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 274px;" /></strong></p>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(692, 632, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">毛孔粗大</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>双均治疗毛孔粗大的效果</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>毛孔粗大 ：治疗2次后效果</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-1605111010115H.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 181px;" /><br />\r\n	<strong>毛孔粗大 ：治疗1次后效果</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-16051110101WZ.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 180px;" /><br />\r\n	<strong>毛孔粗大 ：治疗1次后效果</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511101026361.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 179px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>双均医学治疗毛孔粗大</strong></div>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong>1、VISIA皮肤检测</strong><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		用VISIA皮肤检测，根据不同的肤质，判断针对性治疗方案，显微镜下的拍照和效果，直观用肉眼看不到的皮肤动态。<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511101036236.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 298px;" /><br />\r\n		<strong>2、OPT治疗方案</strong><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		双均OPT王者风范技术，采用特定的宽光谱彩光，直接照射于皮肤表面，并穿透至皮肤深层、选择性作用于皮下色素或血管，同时刺激皮下胶原蛋白增生、促进皮肤胶原纤维收缩，改善造血和皮肤微循环功能，促进皮肤新陈代谢，让皮肤产生紧致效果，从而有效的收缩毛孔。<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511101043964.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 310px;" /><br />\r\n		<strong>3、快速性解决各种问题</strong><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		缩小毛孔同时可以治疗，皮肤粗糙，痘痘，痘坑，痘疤，面部细纹等肌肤问题，1次医学治疗，等于4000次的日常护理。<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511101051226.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 144px;" /><br />\r\n		<strong>双均医学治疗毛孔粗大过程</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<center>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511101100408.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 311px;" /><br />\r\n		<