(693, 632, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong><span class="label-box-txt bgrded">祛黄褐斑</span></strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R425501.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　双均祛黄褐斑的效果</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<div>\r\n		　　<strong>深皮层黄褐斑：</strong>治疗4次&nbsp;<br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R43X22.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 276px;" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		　　<strong>表皮层黄褐斑：</strong>治疗3次</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R445596.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 276px;" /></p>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<br />\r\n		<strong>双均祛黄褐斑为什么会不反弹</strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<br />\r\n		<span style="text-align: left;">　　主要以高度集中的辐射能量及色素选择性，使激光能量集中作用于色素颗粒，将其直接击碎，通过淋巴组织使黑色素全部排出体外。</span></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　激光能量溶解深层黑色素</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R452214.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 212px;" /></strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　排除深层沉积黄褐斑</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R45cC.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 256px;" /></strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　只有做到这3步 才能根治不反弹</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　1、皮肤检测</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong style="text-align: center;">　　</strong>用VISIA皮肤检测，根据不同的肤质，检测你的黄褐斑是处于表皮层斑，还是深皮层，处于表皮层的黄褐斑，治疗3次即可，如果处于深皮层治疗次数需要4-5次，才能彻底祛除不再复发。</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R50EM.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 341px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>　　2、击破黑色素</strong><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<strong>　　</strong>532纳米激光直接打入皮肤内层100um处，击破黑色素细胞，激光只被相应颜色的色素吸收，只有病变的细胞才吸收特定的激光，所以对皮肤组织没有任何损伤。</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R51L07.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 336px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong><span style="text-align: left;">　　3、美肤</span></strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		　　祛黄褐斑同时促进胶原再生，收缩毛孔，根据深浅程度治疗后黄褐斑逐渐消失，皮肤干净白暂，细腻光滑。治疗后不影响出门及工作</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R5253K.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 343px;" /></p>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong>双均祛黄褐斑治疗过程</strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong style="text-align: left;">看到镜中脸上的黄褐斑，心情无比沮丧</strong><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R543157.jpg" style="width: 391px; height: 396px;" /><br />\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>专家进行皮肤诊断</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R550354.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 350px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>综合治疗方案</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R55K32.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 350px;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>黄褐斑祛除后，脸上露出久违的笑容</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R610296.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 276px;" /></p>\r\n', '', '', '127.0.0.1'),
(694, 621, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>面部脂肪塑形</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051009564V40.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　现在小脸当道，爱美人士都瘦脸成风，如果面部的脂肪太多，就会让整个脸看起来很不美观。盘点那些个小脸明星，他们是否天生养成?</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095AI46.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 317px;" /><br />\r\n	<a>姑凉们，为了变美，咱是不是该做点啥?</a><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　双均Plasma等离子激光溶脂</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　通过负压吸脂、超声吸脂、电子吸脂或共振面部吸脂等手术方法将脂肪细胞吸出，达到修复脸型、重塑面部轮廓的作用。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095G2X7.jpg" style="width: 445px; height: 110px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　手术过程</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095H0561.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 112px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　<strong>　恢复时间</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="text-align: center;">　　手术后7天就可以正常生活,进食无任何限制;一般来说，手术后6周，所有后遗症消失。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong style="text-align: center;">双均吸脂瘦身保障</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095I1624.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 259px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　1、量身打造适合项目</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均通过为患者设计的瘦身诊疗系统打造适合的肥胖治疗效果，如定制衣服一般合身。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095J01J.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 260px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　2、专业的医疗设备</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均源源不断的引进专业化的医疗设备，追求冷冻脂肪破坏术、高频等先进治疗仪器。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095K3225.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 260px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　3、简单快捷无副作用</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均吸脂瘦身几乎没有痛症和副作用，是一项非常简单便利的瘦身治疗方法。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095P1E9.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 260px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　4、具备完整的安全体系</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　双均整形认为，安全高于一切。吸脂手术过程中即使发生停电也可以供应应急发电系统应对。</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　双均经典案例<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095Q1112.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 279px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510095S0945.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 279px;" /></strong></div>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(695, 621, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>自体脂肪丰太阳穴</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510143305120.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;　　太阳穴不丰满，给人不舒服的感觉，在中国人的传统审美观中，丰盈饱满的额头象征着智慧和福禄，太阳穴凹陷的人，给人感觉不好相处、尖酸刻薄。因此，当太阳穴有缺陷时，可以采用丰太阳穴来进行改善。</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510143316104.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 279px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101433244U.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 254px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　自体脂肪丰太阳穴</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　安全、有效、持久、自然、细胞保存</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　手感触觉：★★★★★</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　形态稳定：★★★★★</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　相容性：★★★★★</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　防渗漏：★★★★★<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　双均自体脂肪移植优势</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　抽取技术：鲜活提取</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510143333C2.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 183px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　要选择较好的脂肪供应区，对脂肪进行鲜活提取创新科技处理，全程采用国外先进的Bodytite去脂设备和网状超平吸脂技术，安全快速提取具有活力优质脂肪颗粒。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　活化技术：鲜活提炼</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101433411U.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 180px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　&ldquo;离心+自体脂肪+生长因子&rdquo;全封闭三联鲜活处理。吸脂后对脂肪进行鲜活提炼创新处理，全面激活脂肪颗粒，使其拥有高度的生物活性，从而具备高度的修复能力和再生能力。确保一次鲜活移植，脂肪成活率就能达到95%以上。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　注射技术：鲜活植入</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051014334a25.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 182px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　要三维多层次立体注射技术，多点位交叉注射，微量多点式注射，让高活性脂肪细胞的分布更加均匀，准确到纳米的剂量控制，这样可完全避免传统术式出现的注射后脂肪堆积的现象。术后皮肤光滑细腻，自然平整无凹凸。</p>\r\n', '', '', '222.210.216.78'),
(696, 621, '<div class="label-box" style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="font-size:24px;"><strong>大腿塑形</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510111339459.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n	修长的双腿能增加女性身材的挺拔、魅力及性感,然而对腿部不够完美(臃肿、肥胖、畸形)的女性来说,夏季是一段尴尬的时光。</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510111529637.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 306px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　想拥有一双高挑迷人的双腿，是每一个爱美的女性梦寐以求的事，然而、有时候上天总是事与愿违!你属于以下哪种症状?<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510111543M4.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 96px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101115514Q.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 96px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101115593B.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 95px;" /><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051011160U29.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 95px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　<a>其实，瘦腿轻而易举，只要&hellip;</a><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong>　　射频溶脂术<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510111616362.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 258px;" /></strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　根据人体比例，用美学将腿部重新设计,在全麻或局麻的情况下，将腿部臃肿、肥胖的脂肪吸出，去除臀部与腿部之间多余的坠肉，从而达到腿部的修长的效果。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510111624316.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 125px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	　　吸脂后，人体内大脂肪细胞数目大大减少，只要求美者不暴饮暴食并进行适度的运动;吸脂塑身的效果可以一直保持下去、不会出现反弹。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>双均吸脂瘦身特色保障<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img a