(32, 5, 5, 1, '双眼皮', '{cmspath}/ybzx/syp', -1, 'index.html', 0, 1, -1, 0, 0, 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/article_tsfw.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '双眼皮', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '0', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111201546.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px" /></div>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　　　</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>双眼皮的分类</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　双眼皮大体分为内双眼皮和外双眼皮两种，还有一种介于内双与外双之间，双均将它叫为内外双眼皮或中间类型的双眼皮。对同一双眼皮眼睛来说，即使只改变双眼皮的模样也会产生不同的感觉。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911121W18.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 291px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　双眼皮类型选择</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 双眼皮类型并不是您想要做哪个就能做出来的，也不是别人说哪种弧线好，就可以适合您，与手术美学设计沟通并确认术后效果非常必要。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>双眼皮宽度的选择</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 双眼皮宽度分睁眼宽度与闭眼宽度。对于亚洲人来说，闭眼后双眼皮宽度7-8毫米为适当范围。但具体需要根据每个人的眼型特征做调整<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　</p>\r\n			<center>\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111415E4.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 321px" /></center>\r\n			<section id="1_290" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.">\r\n				<section>\r\n					<div style="text-align: center">\r\n						<br />\r\n						<a><span style="color: #ff0000">详情点击咨询</span></a></div>\r\n				</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>　　找到适合您的双眼皮手术方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　1、<strong>20-28岁双眼皮手术方法</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 手术适应症：单眼皮，小眼睛变大眼睛需求，轻度内眦赘皮、外眦赘皮睑板短窄、眼距过宽等问题。</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　美学设计指导：年轻女性眼部皮肤支撑力好，无论做切开还是埋线都可以实现良好的小眼放大效果，只要解决好附带的内眦赘皮问题，就可以放大双眼<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911152bH.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 156px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　手术示意<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111540I4.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　2、28-38岁适合的双眼皮手术</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 方法手术适应症：眼部衰老、轻中度上眼睑松弛、眼袋等问题</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　美学设计指导：这个时期的女性皮肤稍显松弛，做双眼皮同时需同期考虑到松弛皮肤的切除等问题，包括眼部除皱。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911154HA.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 126px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　手术过程<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111555C1.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 170px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　3、38-48岁双眼皮手术</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 方案手术适应症：眼袋、泪沟、皱纹以及中面部松弛下垂的问题</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　美学设计指导：需要进行眼部美容与抗衰，同期需考虑脂肪移植填充的需要<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111602Z1.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 132px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　手术过程<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-1605091116104R.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 128px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<section id="1_290" label="Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.">\r\n				<section>\r\n					<div style="text-align: center">\r\n						<a><span style="color: #ff0000">详情点击咨询</span></a></div>\r\n				</section>\r\n			</section>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>　　双均双眼皮综合整形案例</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>　　美眼榜样</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　1、术前：美学设计美眼，量身定制美眼方案</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-1605091116191U.jpg" style="width: 482px; height: 159px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　2、术中：国外技术，精细好<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911162GL.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 291px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　3、术后1-7天快速恢复，好塑造美眼<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111635513.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 322px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>双均眼部整形承诺</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>1、个性化定制美眼方案</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;眼睛只是有双眼皮并不漂亮，根据需要，恰当的切除脂肪和在定位，增加内外眼角长度并通过眼部除皱等方式，找出眼睛目前的缺点和优点并进行彻头彻尾的分析，做出合适的眼睛形状。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　2、双均眼部整形不是追求人造美，而是自然造美。</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111643114.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 319px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　3、专精于眼部手术的美学设计实施</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509111A12P.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 319px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>4、不忘记作为医疗队伍对医疗结果的责任</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;对于手术结果的副作用，不满意等术后护理问题，我们比其他医院本着更高的道德上、医学上的标准来积极解决。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　5、用心聆听患者和顾客的声音</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 无论何时都会站在患者的立场上，就算是小事也不会置之不理。&ldquo;一切以顾客的需求为根本，为帮助顾客实现积极的人生梦想而服务&rdquo;是双均不变的宗旨。</p>\r\n			<blockquote>\r\n				责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/yanbuzx/shuangyanpi.jpg'),
(33, 5, 5, 2, '开眼角', '{cmspath}/ybzx/kyj', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/article_tsfw.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '开眼角', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '0', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center">\r\n				&nbsp;<span style="text-align: center">&nbsp;　　</span><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112031D4.jpg" style="text-align: center; width: 500px; height: 313px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;双均分型开眼角手法方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　开外眼角</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>适应症：</strong>严重的外眦赘皮或伴发邻近部位畸形者<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>手术方案：</strong>单纯进行外眦成形术，单眼皮者可同时进行开外眼角与双眼皮手术。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　开内眼角</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112042O8.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 124px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>适应症：</strong>双眼间距过宽者，有内眦赘皮者，先天性小眼症者<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>手术方案：</strong>双均引进的原创无痕开眼角手术，无需切开眼底，使疤痕无法产生在眼底，从而解决基本的问题，使用了极少量线结，术后直观眼睛自然美观。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　双均专业医师精心设计、精微操作</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112051154.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 243px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				　　制定详细手术方案 &nbsp;对眼睛进行精密设计 整体调节,外眼角<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911205T59.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 246px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				　　上一步的外眼角与这一步的内眼角手术同时进行 双均独特护理</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				　　(7天恢复)<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>精细内切眼角</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>无痕内切技术：</strong>内切技术可以调整双眼的大小，两只内眼角在48&deg;左右。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　医师指导：</strong>眼睛柔不柔美一眼就看的出来，不仅是精细化无痕手术，传神的眼睛才是眼部整形理念的真谛。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911210N41.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 140px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　手术过程</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112116291.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 244px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				　　制定详细手术方案 1mm无痕切割去除脂肪</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911212N49.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 247px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				　　对伤口精细缝合 对伤口精细缝合<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>无痕外切眼角</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 五官横比例定位技术：</strong>我们的五官比例，眼睛横向比例在全脸的3分之1处 ，开外眼角可调节脸型。<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				　<strong>　双均指导：</strong>每个人的脸型都不一样，针对脸型的不同，通过控制外眼角的高低，对整个脸型气质进行精细打造。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112135251.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 142px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　手术过程</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112143246.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 248px" /><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				制定详细手术方案 精细眼尾切开，不多1mm不少1mm<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112152R1.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 244px" />　　<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				完美比例去脂，精细缝合 双均独特护理(7天恢复)<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<a>详情请点击咨询</a><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>　　双均精细的眼部美学设计</strong></p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>　　成就七天术后不一样的你</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>立体：</strong>多元化眼部设计，个性化定制<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911220O39.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 194px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　精塑：</strong>精微到毫米的点睛数<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112214233.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 289px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>微创：</strong>国外潮流技术，无创伤<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112222364.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 323px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>美眼：</strong>术后100%自然灵动<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112230L9.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 95px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<a>详情点击咨询</a><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<strong>双均眼部整形承诺</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　1、个性化定制美眼方案</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 眼睛只是有双眼皮并不漂亮，根据需要，恰当的切除脂肪和在定位，增加内外眼角长度并通过眼部除皱等方式，找出眼睛目前的缺点和优点并进行彻头彻尾的分析，做出合适的眼睛形状。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　2、双均眼部整形不是追求人造美，而是自然造美。</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050911223R17.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 318px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　3、专精于眼部手术的医师实施</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509112251O1.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 316px" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>4、不忘记作为医疗队伍对医疗结果的责任</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 对于手术结果的副作用，不满意等术后护理问题，我们比其他医院本着更高的道德上、医学上的标准来积极解决。<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				　　<strong>5、用心聆听患者和顾客的声音</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;无论何时都会站在患者的立场上，就算是小事也不会置之不理。&ldquo;一切以顾客的需求为根本，为帮助顾客实现积极的人生梦想而服务&rdquo;是双均不变的宗旨。</p>\r\n			<blockquote>\r\n				责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/yanbuzx/kaiyanjiao.jpg');
