(507, 6, 4, 50, '蒜头鼻整形', '{cmspath}/bbzx/suantoubzx', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/article_tsfw.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050915101BR.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 262px;" />　　<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>蒜头鼻的症状<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509151025543.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 230px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>真人案例</strong></div>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-1605091510332U.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 365px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　宽大的鼻梁给人厚重、笨拙的感觉，且面部失去柔和美。需要针对具体的宽鼻情况，进行针对性矫正。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　手术方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　1、鼻翼软骨内收缝合术：</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　采用鼻小柱横切口或&ldquo;V&rdquo;切口，显露两侧鼻翼软骨，将鼻翼软骨内收缝合。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509151045640.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 188px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　2、鼻尖软骨增高术：</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　使用自身软骨代替人工假体，用筋膜包裹手术部位，副作用极小综合调剂鼻头高度、角度与模样，塑造自然美鼻。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509151052956.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 197px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　3、鼻头部软组织厚切除术：</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　去除皮下组织与多余的肉，增高鼻头。同时进行将耳软骨、鼻中隔软骨植入鼻头，塑造高耸鼻梁。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-160509151103G6.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 188px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　手术信息</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160509/1-16050915111Ga.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 263px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<a>详情点击咨询</a><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均隆鼻手术原则</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　1、选择适合顾客的手术方法</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　根据每个患者的特征做不同的手术方法，选择漂亮的鼻部曲线，给您提供满意的手术效果。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　2、选择肤质和鼻子的模样相配的安全填充物</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　鼻部皮肤或厚、或薄、或透亮，鼻梁的骨质情况也各不相同，双均根据多样化的人体特征选择适合的硅胶、字体、筋膜材料进行恰当的组合，将效果优化。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　3、强调和润挺翘的鼻尖风格。</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　无论做任何鼻部项目，都注重鼻尖形态的塑造。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　4、为了减少炎症发生，配备彻底的灭菌、消毒系统。</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　双均所有手术道具都通过高压灭菌和气体消毒处理。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　5、尽量限度减少疤痕</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　尽量采用使开刀的疤痕看不见或缩小的方法进行手术，手术后照顾到减轻疤痕的问题。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　6、尽量减少组织受损，一同解决浮肿问题，把恢复时间缩到很短。</strong></p>\r\n			<blockquote>\r\n				责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/bibuzx/project_58.jpg'),
(508, 6, 4, 50, '鹰钩鼻整形', '{cmspath}/bbzx/yinggoubzx', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/list_tsfw.htm', 'dzsjyy/article_tsfw.htm', '{typedir}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;　　<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512141440923.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 339px;" /><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>鹰钩鼻的症状<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF21J34.jpg" style="width: 115px; height: 139px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF234W9.jpg" style="width: 115px; height: 140px;" /><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF255360.jpg" style="width: 115px; height: 139px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				　　鼻翼软骨中间脚向下过度生长或内侧脚过长。鼻中隔软骨过长。鼻中隔降肌肥大。<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>手术方式</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF403438.jpg" style="width: 253px; height: 79px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　经鼻孔缘切口，切除过长的两侧鼻软骨下端或鼻翼软骨外侧角上段及外侧部。此法亦适用于鼻尖缩小整形。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF553T3.jpg" style="width: 253px; height: 91px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　切除过长的鼻中隔软骨：通过中隔前缘纵形切口，切出不同方向过长的中隔软骨，以矫正相应部位的隆起畸形。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/150817/1-150QGF602243.jpg" style="width: 253px; height: 80px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　切断肥大增生的鼻中隔降肌：在口轮匝肌深层紧贴上颌骨切牙窝