(540, 9, 4, 50, '脂肪移植', '{cmspath}/xzss/zifangyz', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150555307.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			&nbsp;　　随着年龄的渐长，面部不可避免地衰老，额头、太阳穴、脸颊等逐渐出现了凹陷、皱纹，胸部也渐渐的萎缩。另一方面由于不正确的生活习惯，身上也囤积了不少的脂肪，样样让人痛不欲生。\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150603427.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 282px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均&mdash;自体脂肪鲜活移植<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150611392.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 520px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　双均自体脂肪鲜活移植，从人体自身某些部位吸取多余的皮下脂肪细胞，纯化处理后注射到额部、胸部，苹果肌，就能立马立体五官，魔鬼身材，完美说明放对地方，脂肪就能变废为宝!<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均自体脂肪移植 取于自体取悦自己</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　1、遇见更精致的自己</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-160510150620340.jpg" style="width: 490px; height: 262px;" /></p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				　　一改刻薄不易亲近的印象，饱满太阳穴，让面部轮廓线条感十足。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-16051015062O27.jpg" style="width: 484px; height: 259px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				　　玻尿酸无法匹及的终身效果，大胆说出我的鼻子完全自体。<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/