(565, 12, 4, 50, '祛痘印', '{cmspath}/pifumr/qudouyin', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q60c42.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 320px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;　<strong>　在双均彻底摆脱痘印烦恼<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q616455.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 257px;" /><br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q623550.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 258px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　你也可以像他们一样恢复光滑肌肤</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　秘诀就在于双均无痕祛痘印<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　分清三类痘印 对症治疗</strong></p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　祛痘印的同时，祛除痘痘根源问题<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q6304J.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 153px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　双均推荐方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q63JY.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 151px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　针对这种复发性的情况，应先彻底祛除根源问题，再去解决表面遗留问题。双均采用光动力LED光疗修改，能够杀死痤疮杆菌和消除炎症，阻断造成痘痘反复发作的皮肤根源问题。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101Q6433E.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 153px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　双均推荐方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QA5604.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 151px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　痘印是痤疮造成的色素沉着，随着皮肤的新陈代谢痘印会慢慢淡 化、变浅，自然淡化需要1~2年。但是，如果不采用医学手段， 痘印仍然是持久性的，不会恢复到长痤疮前的颜色。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QF5209.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 159px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　双均推荐方案</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QG3R2.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 327px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　痤疮凹洞是因为严重痤疮或挤痘痘不当引起的真皮塌陷， 痤疮凹洞一旦产生就不会自动消失，双均已经找到了解决的办法。</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　(以上是推荐方案，具体个性化的治疗方法需与医师面诊。)<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　痘印越早祛除越好</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　随着年龄的增长，痘印的色素沉着，皮肤层色素沉积的越来越深，痘印不仅是影响美观，还会加速皮肤老化，使整个人呈老态。祛除痘痘的同时，彻底祛除痘印根源，是解决皮肤问题的真正所在!<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均祛痘印怎么样<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QH1606.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 164px;" /></strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　双均无痕祛痘印采用光学物理疗法，祛痘印的同时不伤肤，彻底解决痘印深层问题，并刺激皮肤产生胶原蛋白，使皮肤细腻光滑。相比传统祛痘印方法更安全有效。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　精彩案例</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QI0392.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 242px;" /><br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101QIK36.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 242px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong><a>详情点击咨询</a></strong></p>\r\n			<blockquote>\r\n				责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/pifumr/project_360.jpg'),
(566, 12, 4, 50, '祛黄褐斑', '{cmspath}/pifumr/quban', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R425501.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 313px;" /><br />\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong>　　双均祛黄褐斑的效果</strong><br />\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<div style="text-align: left;">\r\n					　　<strong>深皮层黄褐斑：</strong>治疗4次&nbsp;<br />\r\n					&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R43X22.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 276px;" /><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n					　　<strong>表皮层黄褐斑：</strong>治疗3次</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R445596.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 276px;" /></p>\r\n				<br />\r\n				<strong>双均祛黄褐斑为什么会不反弹</strong>\r\n				<div style="text-align: left;">\r\n					<br />\r\n					<span style="text-align: left;">　　主要以高度集中的辐射能量及色素选择性，使激光能量集中作用于色素颗粒，将其直接击碎，通过淋巴组织使黑色素全部排出体外。</span></div>\r\n				<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n					<strong>　　激光能量溶解深层黑色素</strong><br />\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R452214.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 212px;" /></strong></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n					<strong>　　排除深层沉积黄褐斑</strong></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160510/1-1605101R45cC.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 256px;" /></strong></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong>　　只有做到这3步 才能根治不反弹</strong><br />\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n		