(577, 12, 4, 50, '祛痣', '{cmspath}/pifumr/quzhi', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104423638.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 310px;" /><br />\r\n				<strong>别把黑痣不当回事</strong></div>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　不要拿黑痣不当回事，由于恶性黑色素瘤几乎60%是由黑痣恶变而来，所以如何识别黑痣恶变，对于黑色素瘤的早期诊断尤为重要。</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　祛痣前，请分清它的真面目<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　交界痣</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　交界痣的痣细胞具有增生活跃的特性，有转变为恶性黑瘤的可能。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-1605111044322H.jpg" style="width: 420px; height: 425px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　皮内痣</strong></p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　为大痣细胞分化而来，是更成熟的小痣细胞，并进入真皮及其周围结缔组织中。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104439150.jpg" style="width: 220px; height: 163px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　混合痣</strong></p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　混合痣是痣细胞巢位于表皮和真皮，稍隆起或呈乳头状，具有恶变倾向。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-16051110444Y01.jpg" style="width: 168px; height: 158px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　对于长在身体易受摩擦或损伤部位的黑毛痣则更要小心，当心它别成为毁你容颜的凶手。<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均祛痣神器&mdash;&mdash;激光</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　国外FDA认证</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　专利技术</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104456451.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 398px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>见效率高</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104504T8.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 300px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　痕</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104512340.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 234px;" /><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104519517.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 300px;" /></p>\r\n			<blockquote>\r\n				责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/pifumr/project_361.jpg'),
(578, 12, 4, 50, '祛胎记', '{cmspath}/pifumr/qutaiji', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '<div class="wrapper-content-tpls">\r\n	<div class="commitment-content">\r\n		<div class="txt clearfix">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104J53G.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 400px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			&nbsp;　　祛胎记是利用高强度的激光照射胎记部位，激光瞬间产生高能量，将胎记的色素颗粒崩解汽化，由体内吞噬细胞吞噬，之后随着人体新城代谢排除体外，色素会随之消失，从而达到去除胎记的目的。\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　太田痣治疗后</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104K1626.jpg" style="width: 567px; height: 207px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　鲜红斑痣治疗后</strong><br />\r\n				<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104KU60.jpg" style="width: 568px; height: 310px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　<strong>咖啡斑治疗后</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104PBK.jpg" style="width: 566px; height: 232px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　<strong>　双均治疗胎记美学设计提醒</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160511/1-160511104Q3405.jpg" style="width: 640px; height: 526px;" /><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n				<strong>　　双均祛胎记</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<strong>　　见效率高</strong><br />\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				　　为顾客设定三次&ldquo;Q核&rdquo;激光的治疗，胎记都能够有效击碎。&ldquo;Q核&rdquo;激光治疗期间的IPL光学嫩肤，可巩固治疗效果，面部肌肤水疗及专业基因修护敷膜组合，能够有效缓解激光治疗所带来的不适，保护敏感肌肤，逐步改善肤质。<br />\r\n				&nb