(590, 11, 4, 50, 'BOTOX', '{cmspath}/weizx/BOTOX', -1, 'index.html', 1, 1, -1, 0, 0, '{style}/index_article.htm', '{style}/list_article.htm', '{style}/article_article.htm', '{typedir}/{Y}/{M}{D}/{aid}.html', '{typedir}/list_{tid}_{page}.html', 'default', '', '', '', 0, '{cmspath}/a/chanpinxilie', '', 0, 0, '', '&nbsp; 走在人群中，放眼望去全是美腿+V脸，内心是不是艳羡无比？与其羡慕别人，不如改变自己，BOTOX轻松帮你实现纤细长腿与精致瓜子脸的美梦！\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong><a href="http://www.bjyestar.com/zixun/"><span style="color:#ff0000;">BOTOX是什么 咨询美学设计</span></a></strong></span>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 什么是BOTOX?</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G42942463.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 403px;" /></strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; BOTOX是先进得到中国SFDA批准的A型肉毒素针剂，并率先进驻双均.注射BOTOX瘦脸可有效用于治疗食性肌肉肥大，它能够迅速使营养 过剩的肌肉失去部分来自于神经的营养作用，从而让肌肉组织变平、变细，从而达到快速瘦脸的目的，同时注射肉毒素祛皱，还能帮助您消除因为动力而引起的所有 抬头纹、皱眉纹、鱼尾纹，您可以专心思索问题，更自信地笑尽情地表达情感。成为众明星的值得选择瘦脸法宝，同时，BOTOX注射还可用于治疗小腿肌肉肥 大，效果一样无可媲美。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; BOTOX除皱原理</strong>：通过阻断神经与肌肉的神经冲动，适度抑制、收缩肌肉作用的神经，从而起到减弱肌肉力量，消除皱纹的作用。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G432025W.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 287px;" /><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155341306.jpg" style="width: 635px; height: 425px;" /></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;<strong> &nbsp; BOTOX瘦脸原理</strong>：将肉毒毒素注射到咬肌内，通过抑制神经肌接头处乙酰胆碱递质的传递，让咬肌逐渐萎缩而起到瘦脸的效果。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G4343A08.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 251px;" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.bjyestar.com/uploads/allimg/160127/1-16012G43353T5.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 325px;" /></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>BOTOX瘦腿原理</strong>：Botox瘦腿针就是把Botox肉毒素注射入小腿肌肉，从而让小腿肌肉萎缩缩小，它可以针对那些因为小腿肌肉肥大导致的小腿粗壮，有效将小腿瘦下来。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155621337.jpg" style="width: 635px; height: 425px;" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均BOTOX注射美容的优势：</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 瘦脸瘦腿紧致肌肤</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均BOTOX功能强大，用于瘦脸、瘦小腿、除皱治疗均能达到好效果。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 先进美学设计坐诊</strong><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<strong><img alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/160512/3-160512155P34Z.jpg" style="width: 500px; height: 337px;" /></strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 双均先进非手术美容美学设计亲诊，治疗效果，放心。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 随做随走，快速见效</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗时间短，注射仅需10分钟，24小时内便可见效。</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 无恢复期 不影响工作</strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗过程轻松，伤、迹，曲线柔和、效果自然。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	责任塑美 铸就品质</blockquote>\r\n', '', '/uploads/static/chanpin/weizx/project_415.jpg'),
